FBIS4-15926 "drsov071_b_94007" FBIS-SOV-94-071 Daily Report 12 Apr 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Confirmation on Raising Retirement Pensions Confirmation on Raising Retirement Pensions LD1204215194 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1530 GMT 12 Apr 94 LD1204215194 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Text] The Russian Federation Social Security Ministry has confirmed that from May Day, implementation will be continued of President Boris Yeltsin's decree on raising the previously fixed retirement pensions, which started on 1 April. This statement was distributed today in connection with the appearance in some mass media of a so-called denial by Russia's Pension Fund regarding the indexation of pensions on May Day. In short, pensions will go up -- that is the most important thing.
